review_blob: Blond with low alcohol. Sweet flavor, fruit notes. In palate the swetness dominates the taste and nothing to tell about hops. I am not going to repeat this beer.

Nice beer, amber colour a little bit cloudy and fruity and yeast aroma . Flavor as they say it is with hints of toffee but i could not feel the banana. The finish is ligth bitter and an average finish
The most remarkable think about this beer is it incredible Gruyere cheese aroma, nice amber color, with very soft hops at the end and subtle nut taste. Interesting to try
